name: MultiValueMap_putAllTest
description: Unit tests for the putAll method of the MultiValueMap class.

test_cases.name: testPutAll_NewKey
test_cases.description: Tests the putAll method with a new key, ensuring the values are added correctly.

test_cases.name: testPutAll_ExistingKey
test_cases.description: Tests the putAll method with an existing key, ensuring additional values are added correctly.

test_cases.name: testPutAll_NullValues
test_cases.description: Tests the putAll method with null values, ensuring the operation fails and the key is not added.

test_cases.name: testPutAll_EmptyValues
test_cases.description: Tests the putAll method with empty values, ensuring the operation fails and the key is not added.

test_cases.name: testPutAll_AfterRemoveMapping
test_cases.description: Tests the putAll method after a removeMapping operation, ensuring additional values are added correctly.

test_cases.name: testPutAll_WithPut
test_cases.description: Tests the putAll method after a put operation, ensuring additional values are added correctly.
